Here's a simple Java program that demonstrates the use of the `long` data type:

```
public class LongExample {
  public static void main(String[] args) {
    // Declare a long variable
    long largeNumber;

    // Assign a value to the long variable
    largeNumber = 2147483648L;

    // Print the value of the long variable
    System.out.println("The value of the long variable is: " + largeNumber);
  }
}
```
